sequenceDiagram
  participant F as Frontend Library UI
  participant G as Gateway
  participant LS as User Library Service
  participant BS as Book Service
  participant US as User Service
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant AN as Analytics Service

  F->>G: POST /api/library/reading-lists/:id/books
  G->>LS: add books to list
  LS->>US: verify bearer token
  US-->>LS: token valid + userId
  LS->>BS: GET /api/books/:bookId (validate each)
  BS-->>LS: book metadata
  LS->>DB: insert ReadingListBook rows
  LS->>AN: emit READING_LIST_BOOKS_MOVED / CREATED events
  AN-->>LS: ack
  LS-->>F: updated reading list
